description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are seeking a Sonographer to join the Omnes Healthcare Family; become part of a company that makes a difference.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Salary: £45,000 - £75,000 per annum depending on qualifications and experience&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Location: Across our hub locations in North East London&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;em&gt;We have fully COVID compliant infection control policies in place&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Omnes Healthcare Limited are operating within the NHS to provide personalised, quality healthcare services and have been doing so since 2006. We aim to develop supportive, genuine relationships with every patient, physician, nurse and healthcare professional that we come into contact with. We believe each patient is unique and deserves treatment that is both effective, heartfelt and has a positive outcome on their well-being.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;When you join us, you&#39;ll be part of something special–an innovative and rapidly growing organisation where we know that the finest patient care comes from empowering our teams to be the very best at what they do.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What is the purpose of the position?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Omnes Healthcare are looking for an enthusiastic, motivated Sonographer who can provide a high standard of support towards the Ultrasound service.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What are the key responsibilities?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;To assist the Ultrasound Clinical Lead with the organisation and supervision of junior/new staff within ultrasound&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;To provide a high standard of work as agreed by the service demands&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;To ensure that the ultrasound examinations of patients are carried out efficiently, consistent with keeping to the standard required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With the exception of Obstetrics, we offer a full range of ultrasound examinations. The candidates should possess various skills and be experienced in performing/reporting the following sonographic examinations:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Abdominal&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Scrotal&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Renal&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Gynaecology, (Transvaginal, Transabdominal)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;MSK&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Vascular&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What do you need to join the Omnes Healthcare Family?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Current HPCP Registration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ultrasound experience within the UK&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Applicants must be able to scan and report independently but work as part of a team with a Clinical Support Worker&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The successful applicant will have obtained a Postgraduate qualification in Medical Ultrasound and completed a minimum of 900 ultrasound scans reported in the last 12 months.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What Omnes Healthcare will offer you in return?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;25 days holiday plus bank holidays&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An extra day off to celebrate your birthday&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;NHS Discount&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Supporting a team of consultant radiologists&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support clinical worker in every clinic&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use of hospital-standard mobile equipment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in regular clinical meetings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Family friendly policies including flexible working arrangements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;And other benefits&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Apply today if you want to make a difference.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;We believe in innovation; we believe in listening to everyone; we believe in providing quality service; and we believe our employees will help us achieve our mission.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Please be aware that all communications about this vacancy will be received to you via email. Always check your mail box and junk mail folders and provide a UK mobile number if available.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
